# Directory Update Log

A dated, newest-first record of changes to this knowledge bundle, so a reader can see how the catalog evolved without reading the version-control history. `log.md` is a reserved filename and is not itself a concept (it carries no frontmatter). Group entries under an ISO `YYYY-MM-DD` heading and lead each line with a bold change type — **Creation** for a new concept, **Update** for a revision to an existing one — so the kind of change is scannable.

## {{YEAR}}-01-01

- **Creation** — Initialized the OKF knowledge bundle for {{PROJECT_NAME}}: bundle-root `index.md`, the `{{PROJECT_SLUG}}` dataset concept, and its constituent table concepts, generated from `DATA-DICTIONARY.md`.
